// =============================================================================
// core/database/sqlite/native/errors/mod.vr
// =============================================================================
// Layer: 7 (façade — public error-surface)
// Spec: SQLite C API — sqlite3_errcode / sqlite3_extended_errcode /
//       sqlite3_errmsg / sqlite3_errstr / sqlite3_error_offset /
//       sqlite3_system_errno.  Appendix D mirrors these numeric codes.
//
// This catalogue models the *public* error surface seen by embedders,
// distinct from the rich internal `DbError` sums used inside l0–l5
// crates.  The two are bridged at the l7_api boundary.
//
// Submodules:
//   * `code`     — primary + extended code catalogues
//   * `message`  — rendered diagnostic message (+ optional offset)
//   * `engine`   — C-API-aligned accessors
// =============================================================================

module core.database.sqlite.native.errors;

public module code;
public module message;
public module engine;
